data.description: Available on Aug. 13th. Beautiful 4 bedroom 2.5 bath plus loft area home in the heart of Richmond Hill available now! Large open floor plan with laminate wood flooring throughout first floor. Kitchen with granite counter tops, large kitchen island and separate breakfast area. Separate formal dining room and formal sitting area. Spacious living room. Master bedroom with tray ceiling. Master bath offers garden tub with separate shower. Over-sized secondary bedrooms. This home offers tons of storage space. Fenced in back yard with patio.
